import React from 'react'; export const LoginPage = () => { return( <>

This page is still under construction!

I'll list some goals I have for this site so that you know what I'll be working on this winter break

  1. Implement a user and admin system.
  2. Implement Search function.
  3. Arrange exercises on cards rather than a single table according to user preference:

    4. a. Cards can be organized by date, exercise, weight.

    b. Implement auto complete for exercise name if it has been done before.

  4. broaden exercise-tracker theme to be a skill-tracker
  5. supply website with an analytics page

    6. a. Shows graphs of progress over time

    b. Shows macro data ie: progress toward 10,000 hrs. total, weight moved etc

)}
